The funeral arrangements for Baba Alatunse Solomon Abai of Melototah Church of Zion, Papa-Ajao, Mushin, Lagos have been released. He was 70. On Wednesday, there will be a Wake at his Mile 12, Lagos residence.   2023: Ogoni monarchs pledge support for Abe, Tinubu     CSO urges states, parties to adopt Osun APC primary’s model     Lasun declines comment   The following day, his body will leave Lagos for Zion City, Igbobini, Ondo State  where it will lie-in-state. There will be a Service of Songs in the evening till daybreak. - Advertisement - On Friday, there will be a service at Zion City and interment will follow immediately. Guests will be entertained at the same venue. SPONSORED